file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /xai/saliency/lime:
    post:
      tags:
      - local
      summary: Generate a LIME local explanation
      operationId: lime
      requestBody:
        content:
          '*/*':
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Prediction'
        required: true
      responses:
        default:
          description: The saliency explanation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Saliency'
  /xai/tabular/pdp:
    post:
      tags:
      - global
      summary: Generate PDP plots model explanation
      operationId: pdp
      requestBody:
        content:
          '*/*':
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ModelInfo'
        required: true
      responses:
        default:
          description: PDPs for all features in the model
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TabularData'
components:
  schemas:
    Feature:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
          enum:
          - string
          - binary
          - number
          - boolean
          - date
          - uri
          - time
          - duration
          - vector
          - undefined
          - currency
        value:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Value'
    FeatureImportance:
      type: object
      properties:
        feature:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Feature'
        score:
          type: number
          format: double
    Saliency:
      type: object
      properties:
        perFeatureImportance:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/FeatureImportance'
    Value:
      type: object
      properties:
        object:
          type: object
          writeOnly: true
    DataDistribution:
      type: object
      properties:
        featureDistributions:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/FeatureDistribution'
      description: Information about distribution of data used for training a model
    FeatureDistribution:
      type: object
      properties:
        min:
          type: number
          format: double
        max:
          type: number
          format: double
        mean:
          type: number
          format: double
        stdDev:
          type: number
          format: double
    ModelInfo:
      type: object
      properties:
        outputShape:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionOutput'
        version:
          type: string
        trainingDataDistribution:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataDistribution'
        taskType:
          type: string
          enum:
          - CLASSIFICATION
          - REGRESSION
        inputShape:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionInput'
        predictionEndpoint:
          type: string
          format: uri
        name:
          type: string
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
      description: Various information associated to a model
    Output:
      type: object
      properties:
        value:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Value'
        type:
          type: string
          enum:
          - string
          - binary
          - number
          - boolean
          - date
          - uri
          - time
          - duration
          - vector
          - undefined
          - currency
        score:
          type: number
          format: double
    Prediction:
      type: object
      properties:
        modelInfo:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ModelInfo'
        predictionInput:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionInput'
        predictionOutput:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionOutput'
        input:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionInput'
        output:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PredictionOutput'
    PredictionInput:
      type: object
      properties:
        features:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Feature'
    PredictionOutput:
      type: object
      properties:
        predictionOutputs:
          type: array
          writeOnly: true
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Output'
        outputs:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Output'
    TabularData:
      type: object
      properties:
        x:
          type: array
          items:
            type: number
            format: double
        y:
          type: array
          items:
            type: number
            format: double
        feature:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Feature'
